    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>&quot;MESS&quot;</strong> is a multiplayer first-person jailbreak game where strategy, deception, and survival collide in a prison environment.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Step into the role of either a <strong>Warden</strong> or a <strong>Prisoner</strong>. As Wardens, your team must maintain order, ensuring prisoners survive until their scheduled executions. Manage their needs, from hunger and health to mental challenges like asthma, diabetes, and outbreaks of disease. Use your tools wisely—batons, tasers, handcuffs, and the emergency button—to keep the chaos at bay.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3330050/extras/8d9eb72776e7a161811a8e24550ca59a.poster.avif?t=1761693926\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3330050/extras/8d9eb72776e7a161811a8e24550ca59a.webm?t=1761693926\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3330050/extras/8d9eb72776e7a161811a8e24550ca59a.mp4?t=1761693926\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Prisoners, on the other hand, have one goal: escape. They’ll need to disrupt systems, find opportunities, and avoid the Wardens to make their break for freedom. Mistakes can mean being caught or left behind.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3330050/extras/e000518ed2902ddd38785a590f1782d2.poster.avif?t=1761693926\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3330050/extras/e000518ed2902ddd38785a590f1782d2.webm?t=1761693926\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3330050/extras/e000518ed2902ddd38785a590f1782d2.mp4?t=1761693926\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >With Wardens managing the prison and prisoners focused on breaking out, each match is a tense back-and-forth of planning and decisions. The balance between order and escape makes every session tough to manage.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3330050/extras/c655c3f64dea30b8b1d27b30d1fcd726.poster.avif?t=1761693926\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3330050/extras/c655c3f64dea30b8b1d27b30d1fcd726.webm?t=1761693926\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3330050/extras/c655c3f64dea30b8b1d27b30d1fcd726.mp4?t=1761693926\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p>",
